{"type":"text","timestamp":1778697134476,"sessionID":"ses_1dd647e0effeZs5rb4D9DoknQl","part":{"id":"prt_e229c59d1001bYo7JQoTu9xZg3","messageID":"msg_e229baa59001GZEmfHw6GMYZmv","sessionID":"ses_1dd647e0effeZs5rb4D9DoknQl","type":"text","text":"The prior successful micro-opts removed always-present arithmetic/reset/RVFI routing; CPI-oriented and predictor changes mostly regressed. I’m writing a narrow control-state pruning hypothesis that targets unused post-EX control bits rather than adding new behavior.","time":{"start":1778697132497,"end":1778697134475},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0761cc24bb43d7e2016a04c3ac6444819992dbcfce1822dc7f","phase":"commentary"}}}}
