g ID-stage temporary and bundle assignment. Keep\\nLUI behavior unchanged by continuing to set alu_op=ALU_LUI, alu_src=1, and\\nreg_write=1 in the existing validated LUI decode arm. This is a narrow\\nno-CPI micro-optimization that should slightly reduce control-bundle width,\\nregister enables, reset/hold muxing, and decode-to-EX routing pressure while\\npreserving the NRET=1 RVFI contract, trap discipline, memory behavior, and\\nall existing stall/forwarding logic.\\n\", \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 1, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/core_pkg.sv\", \"description\": \"Remove the unused is_lui field from ctrl_t so it no longer propagates throug...","metadata":{"matches":1,"truncated":false},"title":"\"id\": \"hyp-20260513-001-r10s0\".*\"outcome\": \"[^\"]+\"|\"id\": \"hyp-20260513-001-r10s0\".*\"delta_pct\": [^,]+","time":{"start":1778697765171,"end":1778697765187}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0aecb5c7440fcb82016a04c6228d98819b8d7d5fde57a97016"}},"id":"prt_e22a5f76b001sOFoyRSuIhYHUs","sessionID":"ses_1dd5ab9d1ffe2B2A54E2vq8V30","messageID":"msg_e22a5c8990019b1t1y0zqSX2OK"}}
