{"type":"text","timestamp":1778678963999,"sessionID":"ses_1de794152ffeQ1ahYrM2u1ppVx","part":{"id":"prt_e21871705001CcO0HZtz6t08IF","messageID":"msg_e2186eb9d0022IB6QpEZ7GesOv","sessionID":"ses_1de794152ffeQ1ahYrM2u1ppVx","type":"text","text":"Prior micro-opt that succeeded isolated the M-extension cone. The next safest micro-opt is to shorten non-essential always-on timing/control paths without changing CPI-visible behavior, rather than adding predictors or moving branch resolution.","time":{"start":1778678961925,"end":1778678963998},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_029067d672686623016a047cb1cb48819a88fcd875d2c7b286","phase":"commentary"}}}}
