{"type":"text","timestamp":1778682594505,"sessionID":"ses_1de422e1bffe6wzHLoYYx6xJoX","part":{"id":"prt_e21be7bf7001q3PJgC7XF92wh6","messageID":"msg_e21be0081001TSi5n7ih7NOaVk","sessionID":"ses_1de422e1bffe6wzHLoYYx6xJoX","type":"text","text":"The log shows prior micro_opts were the successful M-unit split, a small MEM lane rewrite regression, and a broken source-aware load-use attempt whose lesson says the idea should be isolated from RVFI operand reporting. I’m going to write a narrow retry hypothesis focused only on qualifying the existing load-use interlock with source-use decode, because it targets CPI without adding new bypass or fetch critical-path logic.","time":{"start":1778682592247,"end":1778682594503},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_023e0e32b68726a5016a048ae01bcc8199ab965f8b3e3eee5e","phase":"commentary"}}}}
