uts, load extraction, misalignment traps, hold_wb behavior, and RVFI aligned-memory fields.\"\n+  - file: rtl/core.sv\n+    description: \"Keep top-level RVFI wiring unchanged while adapting to the more isolated MEM/WB execution and RVFI shadow paths.\"\n","additions":17,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r10s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778696184079,"end":1778696184084}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_03b169a42f7f372d016a04bfe51dc08199a7159698b176fe04"}},"id":"prt_e228d9763001arzB6nuBKvUbug","sessionID":"ses_1dd72e6daffec3mB05znqTDbW4","messageID":"msg_e228d627f001vEG8elGJS7rUOt"}}
