plicating it, while EX redirects flush the registered entry\n  and update PC with redirect priority. This should remove the imem-data-to-decoder\n  combinational path and improve Fmax, with only a small CPI risk and no change to\n  the NRET=1 retirement/RVFI contract.\nexpected_impact:","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r11s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778697149253,"end":1778697149256}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_07dfefc7b06bf521016a04c3bc7c6c819bb7a737238d9c787f"}},"id":"prt_e229c98ca001Cfjk6kWm0udkhJ","sessionID":"ses_1dd647d9dffeBsTH93dW9wPxMG","messageID":"msg_e229c7e6f001sH3GLOTVnhhsmC"}}
