rving the current NRET=1 RVFI port set and pipeline control.\"\n","additions":31,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r13s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778698765487,"end":1778698765489}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_00ab77b14caf5196016a04c9f98fa0819b8bcb4729d2cc1424"}},"id":"prt_e22b4f73c001Sa3kVlyAuQgteC","sessionID":"ses_1dd4b95daffeUPuCkcS77kE0Dc","messageID":"msg_e22b49d46001TsrjVIg6OQ5zsn"}}
