{"type":"text","timestamp":1778678954849,"sessionID":"ses_1de7941beffepjxUFM8Diz3UWE","part":{"id":"prt_e2186f967001b3x23fDLFxjqxD","messageID":"msg_e2186e8b9001JR2sbo4kP9fhuG","sessionID":"ses_1de7941beffepjxUFM8Diz3UWE","type":"text","text":"The only prior structural proposal was early ID redirect, and it broke due to stale decode-stage operands. I’ll avoid that path and propose a structural change that targets stall overlap without moving control resolution earlier.","time":{"start":1778678954343,"end":1778678954848},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0f3c58f568d8544a016a047caa34dc819b9d435171d929ec49","phase":"commentary"}}}}
