rd interface; while that\n  bit is set, hold EX/MEM and clear MEM/WB valid exactly as today, but drive the\n  global pipeline stalls from the registered busy state rather than directly\n  from io_dmemReady. Keep dmem_addr, dmem_wdata, dmem_wen, dmem_ren, RVFI memory\n  masks/data, misalignment traps, and all in-order retirement behavior","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r7s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778689171095,"end":1778689171104}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0cdbe51ec00e61d8016a04a491fd20819886481d7ef4a1b0e0"}},"id":"prt_e2222dabf001enasIFIGrukQ7v","sessionID":"ses_1ddde3ef1ffelGBZQCOkrNjfqc","messageID":"msg_e2222c8c6001RHGFMzIypnD11m"}}
