rwarding during dmem stalls.\"\n+  - file: rtl/wb_stage.sv\n+    description: \"Replace the post-MEM/WB mem_to_reg mux with a pass-through of the registered writeback result while preserving write enable and x0 handling.\"\n","additions":33,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r8s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778693403850,"end":1778693403858}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_087594bdf72c7a17016a04b5058cac819a84e7d479b53bfbf3"}},"id":"prt_e22631e07001T8njq3ThvOZxxP","sessionID":"ses_1dd9d6dacffeihw7ZVTZ2qaxYo","messageID":"msg_e22630839001uJMlYWI7zIXcE9"}}
