{"type":"text","timestamp":1778699825562,"sessionID":"ses_1dd3ade52ffeF6Xz7qFVnga0K8","part":{"id":"prt_e22c56a44002Nrt0UV44V1sUYo","messageID":"msg_e22c54dca001M3deS5hA9aa2Hq","sessionID":"ses_1dd3ade52ffeF6Xz7qFVnga0K8","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts all paid too much timing/control cost when adding fetch/decode target machinery. I’m going to propose the narrowest remaining predictor-style change: make the existing static not-taken predictor explicit by suppressing fetch/ID flushes for not-taken conditional branches, which avoids new target state and keeps prediction off the IF path.","time":{"start":1778699823684,"end":1778699825561},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08412fa221217d2f016a04ce2f9448819aad9bfa63290010d8","phase":"commentary"}}}}
