{"type":"text","timestamp":1778678959864,"sessionID":"ses_1de7940d2ffeyK0MHkwxKUwbJa","part":{"id":"prt_e21870d5d001WBLX4EsFODknUr","messageID":"msg_e2186f2a9001pJVuglOjC4V3NX","sessionID":"ses_1de7940d2ffeyK0MHkwxKUwbJa","type":"text","text":"The prior predictor tried full IF-stage BTFNT/JAL prediction and lost Fmax because immediate decode and target adders landed on the fetch PC path. I’m going to propose a narrower predictor: a tiny return-address stack for JALR returns only, avoiding branch immediate decode on IF critical path while targeting CoreMark call/return bubbles.","time":{"start":1778678959453,"end":1778678959863},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0fc8fc6f208efdfb016a047caf4fd08198a9c786491247bddf","phase":"commentary"}}}}
