ire prediction inputs to IF, update it from resolved control-flow events, and preserve the NRET=1 RVFI port contract.\"\n+  - file: rtl/hazard_unit.sv\n+    description: \"Treat return-prediction mismatches like existing EX redirects so wrong-path IF/ID and ID/EX state is flushed without changing data-hazard behavior.\"\n","additions":31,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-003-r2s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778678995725,"end":1778678995727}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_09c4e25c827095c3016a047cbede54819a86f7ca3f4ecc6915"}},"id":"prt_e21874a05001DLS08ZDMqahtyV","sessionID":"ses_1de7940d2ffeyK0MHkwxKUwbJa","messageID":"msg_e2187170d002heJhWl2cCDrryb"}}
