 an already-predicted JAL from an unpredicted redirect.\"\n+  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n+    description: \"Detect legal JAL after decode, compute the PC-relative target from the existing immediate, drive an early redirect, and latch the predicted target metadata.\"\n+  - file: rtl/core.sv\n+    description: \"Wire the ID-stage JAL redirect into IF and hazard flushing with priority below reset and alongside the existing EX redirect path.\"\n+  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n+    description: \"Suppress the normal JAL redirect when the decoded prediction matches the resolved jump target; keep branch, JALR, misalignment, and mismatch recovery unchanged.\"\n","additions":32,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-003-r3s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778680513421,"end":1778680513425}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0aa344690ce82a18016a0482ab35188199aec6e724e5f4916c"}},"id":"prt_e219e6d2100141Onad7u0ZNszE","sessionID":"ses_1de624aedffeUTdz1TO7ZXsmCS","messageID":"msg_e219e65eb001CXwW8prcIrkvLO"}}
