rried prediction exactly matches the resolved next PC.\"\n+  - file: rtl/core.sv\n+    description: \"Wire the JAL predictor update and prediction metadata between IF and EX while preserving the NRET=1 top-level RVFI interface.\"\n","additions":32,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-003-r6s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778687349864,"end":1778687349870}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_03489222b06cb879016a049d61ea50819a8925d83d922a31c8"}},"id":"prt_e2206c736001l6sqA4LMAXjNwm","sessionID":"ses_1ddf9c2e0ffen6zmBpNmqkD6vT","messageID":"msg_e22066b22001vy3EftbRuj3pPJ"}}
