{"type":"text","timestamp":1778693368711,"sessionID":"ses_1dd9d6d28ffeJXmrKozX6DrpvQ","part":{"id":"prt_e2262e6f6001IKge9MNWx6n249","messageID":"msg_e2262cdbf001hiYyZAmADAIdDg","sessionID":"ses_1dd9d6d28ffeJXmrKozX6DrpvQ","type":"text","text":"The predictor history is uniformly negative when anything touches the IF next-PC path. I’m going to propose the narrowest predictor angle left: a decode-stage early redirect for unconditional `JAL` that deliberately avoids IF-side target muxes, BTBs, RAS, counters, and branch prediction.","time":{"start":1778693367542,"end":1778693368709},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_07017aa50c76c82b016a04b4f76e5c8198b3530204ea574e50","phase":"commentary"}}}}
